{"tid":2083490,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"急問！！！請問Thei、Speed、BU CIE邊間有出路？","createTime":"2020-06-28T19:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T02:43:25.000Z","uid":298415,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a8425ffd8460091d6f79c40b77b389d37a9696b6","tid":2083490,"uid":298415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T19:15:03.000Z","msg":"我係今年啱啱讀完 CCCU-CIMP 副學嘅肥妹仔<br />\nGPA: 2.95<br />\n（總合哂兩年，有一個Sem衰咗 2科 必修文科 嘅科目）<br />\n（較為擅長嘅科目主要係 Creative Thinking、Interactive Media Design 果類，打code/programme 較為差）<br />\n（有過過CCCU 比嘅<br />\n<br />\n曾經有報過Poly、BU year3 degree&hellip;類似相關嘅科目<br />\n但係連面試機會都無<br />\n((一定係廢得滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為自己自問讀書都唔叻，所以有去報其他唔同嘅top-up做後備<br />\n而近期收到呢啲offer<br />\n所以我想參考吓各位前輩嘅意見／讀過呢幾間學校嘅人嘅評價<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThei - Multimedia Technology and Innovation <br />\n（創新及多媒體科技）<br />\n<br />\nSpeed - Bachelor of Art in Applied &amp; Media Arts<br />\n（應用和媒體藝術文學）<br />\n<br />\nBU CIE - Social Science in Media and Social Communication <br />\n（媒體及社會傳播社會科學）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我知實有人話呢三間都係&hellip;同一類 垃圾</span></strong><br />\n（自問自己GPA無實力&hellip;攞到8大offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n（有得讀當然讀⋯）<br />\n<br />\n但我覺得如果以 副學 身份出嚟做嘢，未必有更多嘅選擇？<br />\n讀多兩年起碼有更多選擇？<br />\n<br />\n而未來嘅工作我想做media相關嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望各位可以解答thx <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8a